05:08.183 --> 05:10.435
[Ominous instrumental music]

05:15.899 --> 05:17.234
[Doorbell rings]

05:18.569 --> 05:19.736
Craig T. Nelson!

05:20.153 --> 05:21.905
-Are you Peter Griffin?
-Yeah.

05:22.030 --> 05:23.365
Make it quick.

05:23.532 --> 05:25.701
[Cheery instrumental music]

05:26.910 --> 05:29.454
Okay, we're gonna get our show
back on the air...

05:29.538 --> 05:33.041
