09:53.635 --> 09:54.678
Excuse me.

09:54.761 --> 09:57.264
-No calls!
-It's about a dying boy.

09:57.347 --> 09:59.641
Hello? What's he got?

10:00.184 --> 10:01.185
Sounds sexy.

10:01.268 --> 10:03.854
Get me exclusive rights to his death
and you got a deal.

10:04.396 --> 10:07.649
Congratulations,
Gumbel 2 Gumbel is back on the air!

10:07.733 --> 10:08.859
All right, Dad!

10:09.193 --> 10:11.820
