11:42.536 --> 11:43.620
No.

11:43.704 --> 11:44.705
[Laughing]

11:44.830 --> 11:47.499
Boy, your face was priceless
when you thought he was.

11:47.958 --> 11:49.459
[Pretending to cry]

11:50.502 --> 11:51.628
You're a monster.

11:51.712 --> 11:53.672
Chris was in on the whole thing.

11:53.755 --> 11:55.632
Anyway, it's over and done with.

11:55.716 --> 11:57.176
[Guitar playing folk music]

11:57.259 --> 11:58.594
