15:01.818 --> 15:02.861
Oh, yeah.

15:06.698 --> 15:09.868
These poor, deluded people
think you have divine powers.

15:09.952 --> 15:10.994
Praise Peter!

15:11.078 --> 15:13.080
-We are your servants.
-It's a miracle!

15:13.163 --> 15:16.166
What would you have us do,
O great healer of Quahog?

15:16.250 --> 15:19.461
There's really no need to do anything.
Paint my house.

15:19.545 --> 15:21.463
It's bad enough to lie to your family...

15:21.547 --> 15:24.216
